Use the standard library
This is how to get_max_triples of n:
   Remember that result is 0
   Remember that a is 1
   Do this n times:
      Remember that b is 1
      Do this n times:
         Remember that c is 1
         Do this n times:
            When sum of a and b is more than c, then:
               When sum of a and c is more than b, then:
                  When sum of b and c is more than a, then:
                     Remember that p is sum of (sum of a and b) and c
                     When p is at most n, then:
                        Increase result
                     End when
                  End when
               End when
            End when
            Increase c
         End do
         Increase b
      End do
      Increase a
   End do
   The answer is result
